parameters:
I kind of thought it would be nice to live a peaceful life
like this.

\SE\SE[15]Lady Lunaroa! The flower care is finished.
\SE[15]Everyone is growing up healthy and strong.

\SE[14]I will never let Lady Lunaroa's flowers wither until
she wakes up! \SE[10]No, on the contrary, I will make them
grow wildly and surprise Lady Lunaroa when she wakes up!

\SE[16] How about something like growing up to pierce
through the ceiling?! \SE[1] Lady Lunaroa seems to like that
kind of thing, doesn't she? \SE[0] Can I get a Wow, amazing!
from you...?!

\SE[3]Hmm, I wonder if I should give them some nutrients...?
\.I'm not really sure.... \!\SE[2]I'll ask Mom about it
later.

\SE\SE[0]I finished all the laundry for today. \!\SE[0]Do
you need any help with something over there?

\SE\SE[15]Is it already finished...! As expected of Nikita-
san! \SE[15]You're really fast at your work, aren't you!

\SE[16]Hehe~. When it comes to household chores, I'm a
former pro, you know. \SE[0]This kind of thing is a piece of
cake for me.

\SE[2]The next task is... Well, let's see. It's having Lady
Lunaroa do today's exercise... \SE[3]Maybe around 30 minutes
later would be good... Um.

\SE\SE[0]I see, understood. \SE[0]Shall we take a short
break then? \SE[0]How about making some tea and taking a
breather... \SE[59]Ah.

\SE[12]Oh no... I... \SE[43]almost interrupted Tita-chan and
Lunaroa's \SE[14]private 30 minutes together...! \SE[14]I
almost accidentally disturbed them...!!

\SE[10]Hmm...! \.Afterwards, you two young ones should get
along well...! \!\SE[11]Don't worry...! I absolutely won't
interrupt the 30 minutes...!

\SE\SE[15]Don't worry, it's okay. \SE[15]I'm sure Laura will
be lenient if it's just a little kiss.

\SE[21]M-Mou... Nikita-san, you... \SE[43]A k-kiss... it's
too soon for me.

\SE[58] ('Chuu'... that... 'chuu' right...? \SE[42] The one
where lips touch each other... \SE[12] 'Kiss' or 'mouth-to-
mouth' or 'kissing'...)

\SE[22]Haa... Haa...! \SE[13]I-I've been so focused on
taking care of everyone until now, I haven't really thought
about it...

\SE[9]W-What should I do...?! \.Right now, I'm alone with
Lady Lunaroa...? \!\SE[42]W-Wait...\.I suddenly feel
nervous...!

\SE[21]Ahaha...\.It must be troublesome for you too, Nikita-
san, right...? \!\SE[5]For me to have a chu with you...\.I
still think it's too soon...right...?

\SE[6]What does Lady Lunaroa think...? \SE[7]I-I mean, would
she... dislike kissing me?

\SE[28] (Uu...! I can't imagine what kind of answer I'll
get...)

\SE[47]Ah... Lady Lunaroa's eyelashes, they're beautiful...
Her skin is also so smooth, it's mesmerizing to look at...
\SE[46] And her lips, they're so glossy... They're lovely...
\SE[14]Ah, ah...! I really want to chu so badly!!

\SE[28]My body is moving on its own...! \SE[57]I can't take
my eyes off her lips...!! \SE[9]I, I can't stop myself...!!

\SE[68]S-Sorry... Tita... I didn't mean any harm. \SE[45]I
guess... the timing was just bad...

\SE[16]Y-Yeah, that's right. \.We've been alone together for
a long time, so it's natural for \SE[15]something like that
to happen....

\SE[16]D-Don't worry, I'll keep it a secret from Laura...!
\!\SE[15]Well, considering Tita's previous efforts, I think
this is a level that Laura should also be able to
tolerate...!

\SE\SE[12]If it comes to that, I'll be on Tita's side...!
\SE[12]Don't worry...! I'll somehow cover for you...!

\SE[9]No, um... That's not it...! \SE[7]I, I definitely
don't feel that way...!!

\SE[12]I-it's difficult to say but... \!\SE[20]Vita-san...
It's about time...

\SE[16]Oh, right...! Sorry, Tita! I'll borrow Lunaroa for a
bit! \SE[15]I'll return her back soon, so please leave the
continuation for that time!

\SE[7]Huh... Uh...! I don't understand a lot of things!
\SE[9]And there are some really big misunderstandings
too...!!

\SE[17]I'm in a hurry, so sorry! \!\SE[15]I'll buy you some
kind of souvenir!

\SE\SE[2]Ah, Vita! \SE[4]It's about time for our exercise
session, so please help me move my body! \SE\SE[2]Please
take care of me every two hours!!!
\SE[8]Hmm... I wonder if you could do it for me...

\SE[2]It seems like something was noisy... Oh my, \SE[4]what
is this...

It seems to be called a 'life support system.' It appears to
provide the body with necessary nutrients and oxygen.
However, I'm not quite sure about the exact mechanism.
